<Title>De-Clutter Switches</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="2" nbrRequired="0">
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationNote>
<Para>A change in roll mode to TO/GA or HUD TO/GA, or in pitch mode to TO/GA will automatically trigger a HUD transition to the full-symbology mode. In other flight phases, a de-cluttered symbology mode may be reset to full-symbology mode by stowing and re-deploying the HUD combiner.</Para>
</OperationNote>
</DispatchProcedure>
